messages.message:
On a demo with a customer (Taxdown) who are trying to use Build to solve their problem using the same Prompts that they used in Converse. This is a kick-off session for them to evaluate Commercial. Build is failing to find any of the values (I suspect because they were found using Advanced in Converse). This is a resulting in a poor experience for the customer as it is not clear why it isn't working and hurts confidence in this being a reliable tool for them.

What is the status of making Advanced mode possible in Build, and in the meantime how can we make this limitation much clearer?

@Nico @Tom Deaney @Lee @hannah
